"To implement a calculation job, one simply sub classes the "
":py:class:`~aiida.engine.processes.calcjobs.calcjob.CalcJob` process class "
"and implements the "
":py:meth:`~aiida.engine.processes.calcjobs.calcjob.CalcJob.define` method. "
